\[
P(Y_7 \leq 27.3) = \binom{8}{7} (0.7)^7 (0.3)^1 + \binom{8}{8} (0.7)^8 (0.3)^0 = 8 \times (0.7)^7 \times 0.3 + 1 \times (0.7)^8 \times 1.
\]  
